# Time Work — Standard Schedule

## Working schedule (effective time)

- **Working**: 08:30–12:00
- **Lunch break (non-working)**: 12:00–13:00
- **Working**: 13:00–17:30
- Total effective work time: **8 hours/day** (3.5 + 4.5)

## Non-working time rules (must be enforced everywhere)

- **Lunch**: 12:00 → 13:00 is always non-working.
- **After work**: after 17:30 → next day 08:30 is non-working.
- **Sunday**: skip to Monday 08:30.

## Implementation guidance

- Any function that adds durations to time must add **working minutes only**.
- Never “approximate” by adding raw minutes across breaks/off-hours; must iterate schedule blocks.

